{"tid":1809674,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方呼籲市民提供荃灣失蹤女童消息（附圖）","createTime":"2020-01-03T09:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T10:05:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d12834a8c7eb9835efab3e98636b4b9b8d69cedc","tid":1809674,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202001/03/P2020010300549_photo_1170257.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202001%2F03%2FP2020010300549_photo_1170257.jpg&h=ddd31aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民提供荃灣失蹤女童消息（附圖）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  警方今日（一月三日）呼籲市民提供一名在荃灣失蹤女童的消息。<br />\n<br />\n  十四歲女童蘇曉婷於二○一九年十二月八日上午離開其位於二陂坊的住所後便告失蹤，其家人於二○一九年十二月十二日向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n  她身高約一點七米，體重約四十三公斤，瘦身材，長面型，黃皮膚及蓄長直黑髮。她最後露面時身穿黑色上衣、黑色牛仔短褲及黑色和白色運動鞋。<br />\n<br />\n  任何人如有該失蹤女童的消息或曾見過她，請致電三六六一 一一七三、五九六二 七二二三或電郵至rmpu-nts-2@police.gov.hk與新界南總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年1月3日（星期五）<br />\n香港時間16時04分"},{"pid":"1f7d6e44913f47b8cb5f549d7c9ee7821c0291b6","tid":1809674,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"二陂坊 全黑 仲要少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be178ba41d7f40c5cfff4df22d08b738172ceba8","tid":1809674,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f7d6e44913f47b8cb5f549d7c9ee7821c0291b6","tid":1809674,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"二陂坊 全黑 仲要少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"但由班狗呼籲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d7390a73c710d6bc7f54d81b05d3ff83b88e67","tid":1809674,"uid":113784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:35:27.000Z","msg":"基本上如果班狗真係要做 私了 殺人 棄屍 呢啲唔見得光嘅事嘅話<br />\n冇可能按正常程序通報上頭 再通報俾成個警隊<br />\n<br />\n所以有人俾狗殺咗 第二區唔知都唔係冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔可以確定呢位女仔係真。失蹤"},{"pid":"36755bbccf45a85a14fd93ebb2cdd27485d9db40","tid":1809674,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:39:35.000Z","msg":"貓哭老鼠"},{"pid":"e53a36fa0a24d4eae2eafb18b66d4322c51b81d9","tid":1809674,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"14歲女仔身高1&middot;7米<br />\n幾高下"},{"pid":"67919c6faba72ca7fb44f41a487301c97c43226c","tid":1809674,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"一係就比黑警殺左扮搵人好似唔關佢事，一係就用搵失蹤人士做藉口其實就通輯"}]}